snippet.title: Above Snakes - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
In this gameplay trailer for Above Snakes, see how the world is created by placing isometric tiles, check out some exploration and crafting elements, and take a look at some of the dangers in this survival base-building PC game. 

Above Snakes' Kickstarter campaign is now live.
